{"tid":1755633,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［警世］2020要贏 必須警惕有120萬既藍絲票","createTime":"2019-11-25T16:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T16:59:11.000Z","uid":138609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b33135a8f6585f6d68be594fdc057020e9b85253","tid":1755633,"uid":138609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:22:53.000Z","msg":"2015年區選保皇黨有79萬票<br />\n2016年立會保皇黨有87萬票<br />\n今屆比2015區選增加51%<br />\n比2016立會增加37%<br />\n今日香港係已經禮崩樂壞<br />\n卻有4成人企政府個邊<br />\n今次大勝係贏在單議席單票制<br />\n如果場抗爭要贏落去 呢d票爭取唔到<br />\n咁就必須諗辦法分化離間打散佢地<br />\n掌心雷種票老人院以外<br />\n其實真係好多真心藍絲死都支持政府"},{"pid":"1fba43cd82cdff2fa5c218a3bdbd01f095eeca6f","tid":1755633,"uid":273670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbc1830cbfad8c3c7106e3b8bd4e974d49c9721","tid":1755633,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"1成應該係種出黎<br />\n3成係廢老加支那豬"},{"pid":"224f39c19b725b5d0ee0bb5c07ba869bd2e41425","tid":1755633,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:33:24.000Z","msg":"你睇下隔離個洗白POST<br />\n政府搵幾件蛋散上黎洗白<br />\n問題票一日搞唔掂一日都冇可能有真普選<br />\n<br />\n元朗屏山北 問題選票改結果 1票之差<br />\n藍田 問題選票改結果 投票人數不符 <br />\n九龍城愛俊 問題選票改結果 投票人數不符<br />\n愛俊最大問題係有人數住最後一個鐘<br />\n屯門景興 / 連點兩次都唔岩投票人數<br />\n青衣盛康 / 不公開544張問題選票<br />\n深水埗南昌中/ 140張問題選票改結果"},{"pid":"4d48d7a3b4261e8ed2e0757d12e0447658908618","tid":1755633,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:33:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"673d26caed4d2828936baedec088fcc2abd22374","tid":1755633,"uid":147643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028c1f7